  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173940/extras/9358da9a69e05ee5291477a84cbc4acf.avif?t=1736516570\" width=400 height=126 /></span><br>This game is a tutorial for shmup beginners.<br>For many players, the danmaku, or \"bullet hell\" genre can appear daunting and impossible.<br>However, once you know the tricks, you'll see that many danmaku patterns are nowhere near as hard as they seem.<br>This game teaches you all the fundamentals of danmaku you need, from hitboxes to dodging techniques.<br>Grab this tutorial, and get started on your road to the unique joys of danmaku!<br><br>Note: This game is a remaster of the eponymous free game from 2016.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1173940/extras/9358da9a69e05ee5291477a84cbc4acf.avif?t=1736516570\" width=400 height=126 /></span><br>This game is a tutorial for shmup beginners.<br>For many players, the danmaku, or \"bullet hell\" genre can appear daunting and impossible.<br>However, once you know the tricks, you'll see that many danmaku patterns are nowhere near as hard as they seem.<br>This game teaches you all the fundamentals of danmaku you need, from hitboxes to dodging techniques.<br>Grab this tutorial, and get started on your road to the unique joys of danmaku!<br><br>Note: This game is a remaster of the eponymous free game from 2016.",
